divs: Sighting DetailsI looked up at the sound of a small plane and saw behind the plane a two tone gray upside down acorn shaped object decending at a 45 degree angle inthe opposite direction. It was overcast at the time and the object was dull colored I was picking cucumbers at the time.It was creepy. It disappeared behind some trees
